Class Space

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.Model
      • models.Space
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Space>, JsonSerializable

    public class Space
extends Model
implements java.lang.Comparable<Space>
    data model class for a "Space". A Space is a tile in the frontend of a user that belongs to one plugin. Each space has its own access permissions.
